    "description": "你这瓜保熟吗？相信你知道这个梗了，我们打算把它做成一个游戏看看。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/140e4c1682c06d6c69341e4875d3fba6.poster.avif?t=1696944775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/140e4c1682c06d6c69341e4875d3fba6.webm?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/140e4c1682c06d6c69341e4875d3fba6.mp4?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这次你是西瓜摊主，看你如何反杀华强。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/1cd7731bf02515edb24ca09727c23b9f.poster.avif?t=1696944775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/1cd7731bf02515edb24ca09727c23b9f.webm?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/1cd7731bf02515edb24ca09727c23b9f.mp4?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>西瓜摊主可以口喷西瓜籽进行战斗，相信不少小伙伴都有过这个想法，我们可以给西瓜籽升级攻击力，一口一个不是问题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/f515334bb86daab5b9f166bbab6549ee.poster.avif?t=1696944775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/f515334bb86daab5b9f166bbab6549ee.webm?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/f515334bb86daab5b9f166bbab6549ee.mp4?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果打不过你还可以叫人来帮忙，他们可能是隔壁的香蕉摊主，也可能是路边的酒鬼大汉，也可能是广场上喂鸽子的大叔、玩无人机的小女孩、玩水枪的熊孩子、拥有钞能力的撒钱老板、修仙的剑圣、甚至是自己扔飞盘自己接的狗狗！总之各个身怀绝技（手动滑稽）！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/57d0a95517cb791b4f48d2b008e9bcbf.poster.avif?t=1696944775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/57d0a95517cb791b4f48d2b008e9bcbf.webm?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/57d0a95517cb791b4f48d2b008e9bcbf.mp4?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你需要思考用怎样的选人和升级策略来搭配出最佳组合，赢得一次次的胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/19ba57aa56b31888f905f4018f141268.poster.avif?t=1696944775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/19ba57aa56b31888f905f4018f141268.webm?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/19ba57aa56b31888f905f4018f141268.mp4?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>我们还贴心地为你准备了四个技能道具：金瓜粒子、吸铁石、生瓜蛋子、生异形。可以说还原度相当高了（狗头保命）！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/033c29cc3d11d85ae999ab1c34b5cf34.poster.avif?t=1696944775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/033c29cc3d11d85ae999ab1c34b5cf34.webm?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/033c29cc3d11d85ae999ab1c34b5cf34.mp4?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/0f4048aec21f64f23f7efebc536ac109.poster.avif?t=1696944775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/0f4048aec21f64f23f7efebc536ac109.webm?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/0f4048aec21f64f23f7efebc536ac109.mp4?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>来吧，看你能坚持住多久！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/95579e21a2ad4ee92cb0a8d20d29a11c.poster.avif?t=1696944775\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/95579e21a2ad4ee92cb0a8d20d29a11c.webm?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819090/extras/95579e21a2ad4ee92cb0a8d20d29a11c.mp4?t=1696944775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>话说我们睡神飞工作室这还是第一次在Steam平台上发行游戏，了解我们的朋友都知道我们在手机上发布过不少游戏，比如《我飞刀玩得贼6》《我的大刀四十米》《太极迷阵》《魔性建筑工》等等。都不是啥正经游戏，因为我们的理念是：创意为先，万物皆可游戏。 这次试试玩一下华强买瓜这个梗，看能做出个啥样的游戏，祝你玩得开心！",
